 <channel>pecl.php.net</channel>
 <summary>High-performance PHP client for Valkey</summary>
 <description>Valkey GLIDE is a high-performance client library for Valkey, built with Rust core and PHP FFI bindings. It provides better performance, type safety, and cluster support with automatic failover.

Note: After installation, add "extension=valkey_glide" to your php.ini file.</description>
